query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk k) NoHashJoin(k mk mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(k mi_idx mk t) NoMergeJoin(k mi mi_idx mk t it1) NoNestLoop(it1 k mi mi_idx mk t kt) NoMergeJoin(it1 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it2) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS northern_dark_movie
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('hand-to-hand-combat',
'marvel-comics',
'magnet',
'anger')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '6.5'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2004
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('USA',
'English',
'America',
'Norwegian',
'Bulgaria',
'American',
'Denish',
'Germany',
'German',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'tv series'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating';
